<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1964807-reading-the-book-description-this-sounds">Reading the book description, this sounds like another perpetration of the Lost Cause Mythology. For those of you who have read it, would you please let me know? Because, while I&#39;m curious, another book that promotes that the South was doing anything other than rebelling for the right to own black people, is something I am NOT INTERESTED in.</a>
</div>
