<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/34379310-the-republic-for-which-it-stands"><img alt="The Republic for Which It Stands: The United States during Reconstruction and the Gilded Age, 1865-1896" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1492550223l/34379310._SY75_.jpg" />
