<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/71636.Grand_Expectations"><img alt="Grand Expectations: The United States, 1945-1974" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388456649l/71636._SY75_.jpg" />
